<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This guidance is for EU citizens applying to the EU Settlement Scheme.</p>

<p>Your status under the scheme will be recorded electronically on Home Office systems. You can view your status as soon as you get a decision on your application.</p>

<p>You can go to your online profile to:</p>

<ul>
  <li>view your status</li>
  <li>understand your rights</li>
  <li>update your details</li>
</ul>

<p>In the future, you will also be able to prove your rights to others online.</p>
</div>
</div>

